    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Believing parents, you have a responsible work before you to guide the footsteps of your children, even in their religious experience. When they truly love God, they will bless and reverence you for the care which you have manifested for them, and for your faithfulness in restraining their desires and subduing their wills.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">2<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"1T 403.1\" data-link=\"116.1915\">Testimonies for the Church 1:403</span>.</span></a></sup>",
