    "content": "There is a reward when the seed of truth is early sown in the heart and carefully tended.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">3<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"CT 144.1\" data-link=\"23.681\">Counsels to Teachers, Parents, and Students, 144</span>.</span></a></sup>",
