    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "Give your children intellectual culture and moral training. Fortify their young minds with firm, pure principles. While you have opportunity, lay the foundation for a noble manhood and womanhood. Your labor will be rewarded a thousandfold.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">5<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"CT 131.1\" data-link=\"23.612\">Counsels to Teachers, Parents, and Students, 131</span>.</span></a></sup>",
