    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "If she [the true wife and mother] looks to God for her strength and comfort, and in His wisdom and fear seeks to do her daily duty, she will bind her husband to her heart and see her children coming to maturity honorable men and women, having moral stamina to follow the example of their mother.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">7<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"ST 11-29-1877\" data-link=\"820.752\">The Signs of the Times, November 29, 1877</span>.</span></a></sup>",
