    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "The great stimulus to the toiling, burdened mother should be that every child who is trained aright, and who has the inward adorning, the ornament of a meek and quiet spirit, will have a fitness for heaven and will shine in the courts of the Lord.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">8<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"3T 566.1\" data-link=\"119.2664\">Testimonies for the Church 3:566</span>.</span></a></sup>",
