    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "<strong>Reward at the Last Great Day</strong>&mdash;In your work for your children take hold of the mighty power of God. Commit your children to the Lord in prayer. Work earnestly and untiringly for them. God will hear your prayers and will draw them to Himself. Then, at the last great day, you can bring them to God, saying, &ldquo;Here am I, and the children whom Thou hast given me.&rdquo;<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">13<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"Ms 114, 1903\" data-link=\"14068.9441001\">Manuscript 114, 1903</span>.</span></a></sup>",
