    "element_type": "p",
    "element_subtype": "standard-indented",
    "content": "When Samuel shall receive the crown of glory, he will wave it in honor before the throne and gladly acknowledge that the faithful lessons of his mother, through the merits of Christ, have crowned him with immortal glory.<sup class=\"chapterendnote\"><a class=\"chapterendnote\">14<span class=\"chapterendnote\"><span class=\"egwlink egwlink_book\" title=\"HR 3-1-1880\" data-link=\"440.44\">Good Health, March 1, 1880, par. 7</span>.</span></a></sup>",
