    "content": "<strong>Title to Admission to the King&apos;s Palace</strong>&mdash;Let the youth and the little children be taught to choose for themselves that royal robe woven in heaven&apos;s loom, the &ldquo;fine linen, clean and white&rdquo; which all the holy ones of earth will wear. This robe, Christ&apos;s own spotless character, is freely offered to every human being. But all who receive it will receive and wear it here.",
